\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces \textbf  {H$^+$ ions constitute the quantum substrate for classical reality emergence.} (\textbf  {A}) Reality hierarchy spanning 14 orders of magnitude from Planck time ($10^{-43}$ s) to conscious thought ($10^0$ s). H$^+$ coherence (red) operates at 24.6 fs, positioned between quantum foundations and neural timescales. (\textbf  {B}) Reality refresh rate of 4.07 $\times $ 10$^{13}$ Hz (40.6 THz) determined by H$^+$ coherence time, establishing discrete temporal frames for consciousness. (\textbf  {C}) H$^+$-defined reality container (red sphere) provides bounded phase space within which all physical processes occur. (\textbf  {D}) Consciousness emerges as the distance $\mathcal  {C} = ||\mathbf  {P} - \mathbf  {T}||$ between perception ($\mathbf  {P}$, blue) and thought ($\mathbf  {T}$, green) trajectories within the H$^+$ reality container (red wireframe). The 13-order-of-magnitude timescale separation between H$^+$ substrate (24.6 fs) and conscious experience ($\sim $100 ms) explains why subjective awareness appears non-physical despite being entirely classical.}}{8}{figure.1}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:reality_substrate}{{1}{8}{\textbf {H$^+$ ions constitute the quantum substrate for classical reality emergence.} (\textbf {A}) Reality hierarchy spanning 14 orders of magnitude from Planck time ($10^{-43}$ s) to conscious thought ($10^0$ s). H$^+$ coherence (red) operates at 24.6 fs, positioned between quantum foundations and neural timescales. (\textbf {B}) Reality refresh rate of 4.07 $\times $ 10$^{13}$ Hz (40.6 THz) determined by H$^+$ coherence time, establishing discrete temporal frames for consciousness. (\textbf {C}) H$^+$-defined reality container (red sphere) provides bounded phase space within which all physical processes occur. (\textbf {D}) Consciousness emerges as the distance $\mathcal {C} = ||\mathbf {P} - \mathbf {T}||$ between perception ($\mathbf {P}$, blue) and thought ($\mathbf {T}$, green) trajectories within the H$^+$ reality container (red wireframe). The 13-order-of-magnitude timescale separation between H$^+$ substrate (24.6 fs) and conscious experience ($\sim $100 ms) explains why subjective awareness appears non-physical despite being entirely classical}{figure.1}{}}
